{"id":"barkos","term":"Barkos","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Painter, (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Ezra 2:53\">Ezra 2:53</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Nehemiah 7:55\">Neh. 7:55</a>). The father of some of the Nethinim.</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Ezra 2:53","Nehemiah 7:55"]}